9:{"metadata":[["$","title","0",{"children":"Wolf Girl and Black Prince | Global Drama Verse Guide"}],["$","meta","1",{"name":"description","content":"The story centers around Erika Shinohara, a vain 16-year-old girl who tells her friends about her romantic exploits, but she actually has no boyfriend. She claims that a handsome boy in a candid photo is her boyfriend, but it turns out that boy is a schoolmate named Kyouya Sata. She has no choice but to make him her fake boyfriend. Unfortunately, Sata may look like a sweet person, but he is actually an ultra-black-hearted sadist. Sata takes advantage of Erika's weakness and treats her like his dog.\n<br><br>\n(Source: Anime News Network)"}],["$","meta","2",{"name":"keywords","content":"KDrama,Anime,TV Series,Movies,Global Drama,Drama Guide,Watch Online"}],["$","meta","3",{"name":"robots","content":"index, follow"}],["$","link","4",{"rel":"canonical","href":"https://gdvg-ten.vercel.app/series/149775/wolf-girl-and-black-prince"}],["$","meta","5",{"property":"og:title","content":"Wolf Girl and Black Prince"}],["$","meta","6",{"property":"og:description","content":"The story centers around Erika Shinohara, a vain 16-year-old girl who tells her friends about her romantic exploits, but she actually has no boyfriend. She claims that a handsome boy in a candid photo is her boyfriend, but it turns out that boy is a schoolmate named Kyouya Sata. She has no choice but to make him her fake boyfriend. Unfortunately, Sata may look like a sweet person, but he is actually an ultra-black-hearted sadist. Sata takes advantage of Erika's weakness and treats her like his dog.\n<br><br>\n(Source: Anime News Network)"}],["$","meta","7",{"property":"og:url","content":"https://gdvg-ten.vercel.app/series/149775/wolf-girl-and-black-prince"}],["$","meta","8",{"property":"og:image","content":"https://image.tmdb.org/t/p/w500https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/anime/cover/large/bx20701-8tyJFN3soUm0.jpg"}],["$","meta","9",{"property":"og:typ